caption.title: Synonymous substitutions in the HA gene of the Palestinian H3N2 sequences (n = 12).
caption.p: The aa substitutions are presented by their position on the HA gene and by HA1 and HA2 subunits. + = Substitution occurs also in A/Switzerland/9715293/2013(H3N2), vaccine strain 2015/2016, ^ = Substitution occurs also in A/Hong Kong/4801/2014(H3N2), vaccine strain 2016/2017 and 2017/2018.
